          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="si-icon-divider" id="contact_top"></div>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <div id="contact">
        <p>
          <a href="mailto:founders@savageinter.net">Give us an e-holler</a>, or we can grab a coffee near our office in downtown Toronto.
        </p>
        <div class="team-member">
          <img src="/img/team/valkyrie-headshot-300.jpg" />
